                     <interp inst="t18440408-1168-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 2 bowls, value 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 19 pence, 33 halfpence, and 60 farthings; the property of <persName id="t18440408-name-803" type="victimName">
